# FlowDesk — Multi-tenant SaaS Dashboard

A full stack business analytics dashboard where companies sign up
and see only their own data — revenue, orders, and team members.

**Live demo:** https://FlowDesk.netlify.app  
**API:** https://FlowDesk.railway.app

## Tech Stack
- **Backend:** Python, Flask, SQLAlchemy, PostgreSQL
- **Auth:** JWT tokens with Flask-JWT-Extended
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Chart.js
- **Deploy:** Railway (backend + DB), Netlify (frontend)

## Features
- Multi-tenant architecture — each company sees only its own data
- JWT authentication — register, login, protected routes
- Revenue chart, orders table, team management
- REST API with 8 endpoints

## Run locally
\`\`\`bash
git clone https://github.com/you/saas-dashboard
cd saas-dashboard
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env   # fill in your values
flask db upgrade
python seed.py
flask run
\`\`\`